Sabrina LaJuan McWEAY, petitioner,
v.
CITIBANK N.A. No. 13-6748. Supreme Court of the United States Dec. 9, 2013. Case below, 521 Fed.Appx. 784 . Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eleventh Circuit denied. Justice ALITO took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
